               <msContents>
                  <summary>F<locus target="#1r"/>-66r Gospel of John in Mahdar, arranged more than once for the days of the week: Monday (1r), Monday (<locus target="#6v"/>), Saturday (ዘቀዳም, 13r), Saturday (ዘቀዳም, 30r), Tuesday (<locus target="#17r"/>), Wednesday (35r), Wednesday (37r), Saturday (41v), Sunday (42v), Thursday (46r), Friday (57r), Sunday (62v), Wednesday (65r). F<locus target="#66v"/>-78v Prayer of Repentance taken from the 81 Books, ጸሎተ: ንስሐ ዘተቀድሐ እም፹ወ፩ መጸሕፍት, incomplete at the end. F<locus target="#79r"/>-80v Asmat prayer for protection from snow, incomplete at the beginning. Red paper strip with number 5 inside. <locus target="#1r"/> mentions the owner, አቡነ ገብረ መድኀን. <locus target="#66r"/> mentions both the owner, አቡነ ገብረ መድኀን, and the scribe, ገብረ ዋህድ, and to the memory of the soul of ገብረ ተክለ ሃይማኖት.  The word for God is also written in red ink as well as the name of Jesus. Illuminations added recently over text. </summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i1">
                    <locus from="1r" to="67r" facs="005"/>
                    <title type="complete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1693John">Gospel of John</title>
                    
                    <textLang mainLang="gez">Gǝ'ǝz</textLang>
                  </msItem>
                  <msItem xml:id="ms_i2">
                    <locus from="67v" to="79v" facs="072"/>
                    <title type="incomplete" ref="https://betamasaheft.eu/LIT1111Anqasa">ʾAnqaṣa nǝssǝḥā</title>
                    <note>Incomplete at the end</note>
                    <incipit xml:lang="gez">
                      በስመ፡ አብ፡ ወወልድ፡ ወመንፈስ፡ ቅዱስ፡ ፩<choice><sic><hi rend="rubric">አ</hi>አምላክ፡</sic><corr>አምላክ፡</corr></choice>
                      ጸሎተ፡ ንስሐ፡ <choice><sic>ዘቀቀድሐ፡</sic><corr>ዘተቀድሐ፡</corr></choice> እም፹ወ፩፡ መጸሕፍት፡
                      በከመ፡ ኃጢአቱ፡ ዘይሁብ፡ ቀሲስ፡ ጾመ፡ ወጸሎተ፡ ወሰጊደ፡ ለብእሲ፡ ዘኢተምህረ፡ ሶበ፡ ኢወሀበ፡ በከመ፡ አበሳሁ።
                    </incipit>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
